snippet.title: Dauntless - Welcome to Dauntless
snippet.description:
The Dauntless Open Beta is live now!
Download and play for free with your friends and fellow Slayers.

Dauntless is an online co-op action RPG for PC, pitting you against dozens of savage Behemoths.

http://twitter.com/playdauntless
http://instagram.com/playdauntless
http://facebook.com/playdauntless
